Text:
so, why, pray tell have i reached 82.4 % at a steady pace for several hours this aft., only to sit stalled at said 82.4% for over twice that length of time since, with 3 full seeds online and only 4 other peers (leeches) to compete for attention with ?

maybe those who've managed to get this 100% and have stuck around to reciprocate, could open up their clients settings to allow, oh, i dunno, say, one or two more handshakes, for example ...

s h a r i n g  i s  c a r i n g   ! ! ! !  (and vice-versa)
just a thought ...
